page_0: "Friend Crutch: An air elemental was loosed by accident in our laboratory. It flew about, exhibiting the Vitus phenomenon that draws the electric force from the lights and watchers, disabling them for some minutes. All would have been well anon, had not an acolyte doused the elemental with a pail of water.

A surge of lightning burst forth, shattering the watcher. 'Twas surprising the face-shield of the watcher did not absorb the shock. I entreat thee to apply thy Colossus to a mathematical study of this interaction, that we might identify and correct this weakness. This crate holds the watcher fragments for thine examination - Friend Gorrick"
